modName: Female Quarian Face Paint and Eyes
summary: Replaces the first female facepaint with one made to look like Tali\'s forehead lines from ME3. Also replaces the blind eyes to look like what I believe Quarian eyes look like.
descriptionHtml:
Replaces the first female facepaint with one made to look like Tali\'s forehead lines from ME3. Also replaces the blind eyes to look like what I believe Quarian eyes look like. Just place the Data folder into your Skyrim folder.

I recommend using the Tali Armor: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15160/

This is the first thing I ever uploaded to the Nexus. Please tell me if there is something I need to fix or if it causes any problems.
The painting was painted by me. http://bigcman321.deviantart.com/art/Tali-Zorah-Vas-Rannoch-294012029
author: bigCman123
